/china/science/article/3255174/stone-tools-unearthed-china-suggest-ancient-humans-east-asia-were-less-isolated-earlier-believed?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>东亚复杂石器的出现较晚一直被认为是该地区长期与世隔绝的结果，但最近发表的新发现研究挑战了这一理论。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 07:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3255174/stone-tools-unearthed-china-suggest-ancient-humans-east-asia-were-less-isolated-earlier-believed?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>